{"tid":1841020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實WWIII係咪打緊？支国而家係最大贏家","createTime":"2020-01-25T06:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T10:01:03.000Z","uid":210638,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a51ca0793f235997fda9e9c7fbbcd624d753299d","tid":1841020,"uid":210638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"1.通過疫症消滅低端人口<br />\n一車車低端白痴支那人沒學識<br />\n又唔戴罩<br />\n肯定係低端人口<br />\n送去武漢個新醫院<br />\n埋左佢話病死<br />\nWho care<br />\n<br />\n2.p4實驗室整左生化武器發要同你講咩<br />\n甚至人地疫苗都prepare好埋又要同你講？<br />\n等啲低端人口死得七七八八<br />\n香港廢青又死得七七八八<br />\n全球爆發到一個地步<br />\n又攞返疫苗出嚟話成功燃發<br />\n一箭幾雕啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 跟本而家啲感染人士全部都係国安特務嚟<br />\n仼務就係加速疫情蔓延<br />\n將病毒派街坊<br />\n勁過一帶一路<br />\n話唔埋仲可以癱瘓西方敵對勢力<br />\n民間恐慌加疫情嚴重<br />\n隨時經濟下滑<br />\n<br />\n支國沒那那又打贏一場WW<br />\n又可以清理低端<br />\n順便消耗下西方敵對勢力<br />\n爽死"},{"pid":"25dfbcff44948e4107720147461303a37153fb78","tid":1841020,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府不封關不作為<br />\n讓武漢病毒入侵香港<br />\n病毒持有者唔發燒，過關體檢check唔到<br />\n唔封關根本係謀殺香港人<br />\n<br />\n醫護界作為唯一能議價的人<br />\n卻認為罷工乜乜乜，責任攬上自己到<br />\n醫護不作為如同站在政府的一方<br />\n真係枉為人，我呸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">下面兩條片講病毒唔會發燒，過幾日就死</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/5l7bf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F5l7bf&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=f29ffb2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/5l7bf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/t7d44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ft7d44&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=8c77b482\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/t7d44</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片係專家分析<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有兩種冠狀病毒</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=7906954c\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYS7rf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYS7rf7.png&h=fa7cecd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">醫護界唔罷工，下場一定無好結果<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGJ6GOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGJ6GOH.png&h=7d1d1de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/wmdyz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fwmdyz&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=27504e3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/wmdyz</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/bflau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fbflau&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=33498bbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/bflau</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2259370dc43dc3a2991c50cf5eb35d0aa7428d88","tid":1841020,"uid":210638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"醫護請安心擺工<br />\n就算我染病<br />\n沒人醫我都唔會怪你地<br />\n我會衝入狗館狂咳<br />\n<br />\n一切都係為左黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3563fd3cc4372a1fbd42ba62c1aa497ff8d6147","tid":1841020,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"自損三千<br />\n陰謀論咁睇都唔合理，搞臭自己個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d33c33fb97e603e171e1dca8a39055eb6d0c257","tid":1841020,"uid":210638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3563fd3cc4372a1fbd42ba62c1aa497ff8d6147","tid":1841020,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"自損三千<br />\n陰謀論咁睇都唔合理，搞臭自己個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim